    {
      "id": "2z9ri19r0wyojflj",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 284,
      "y": 428,
      "width": 499.65999999999997,
      "height": 148,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 996247159,
      "versionNonce": 1002170859,
      "version": 1,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782051500909,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Ecosystem dominance dynamics   D(t) in R^5\n\nLotka-Volterra competition  ==  online hyper-heuristic\ncompatibility  v_i = cos(V_i, c)      ( V = state prototypes )\nperformance    p   = (CR - FR) . v    boost b = failure spike\nD(t+1) = normalize( clip_[0,1](\n         a.D + eta.A.D - lam.S.D + beta.p + gam.v + del.b ) )\na=.85  eta=lam=.12  beta=.25  gam=.20  del=.20   =>  ||D||_1 = 1",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "originalText": "Ecosystem dominance dynamics   D(t) in R^5\n\nLotka-Volterra competition  ==  online hyper-heuristic\ncompatibility  v_i = cos(V_i, c)      ( V = state prototypes )\nperformance    p   = (CR - FR) . v    boost b = failure spike\nD(t+1) = normalize( clip_[0,1](\n         a.D + eta.A.D - lam.S.D + beta.p + gam.v + del.b ) )\na=.85  eta=lam=.12  beta=.25  gam=.20  del=.20   =>  ||D||_1 = 1",
      "lineHeight": 1.3,
      "baseline": 15
    },
