      "seed": 390887331,
      "versionNonce": 1121481225,
      "version": 1,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782051500909,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Paradigm library   (5 hormones -> 5 allocators; ONE selected)\n\nH_SPATIAL  spatial_greedy : nearest-feasible + reject\nH_CRIT     priority_first : priority-tiered LSA\nH_TEMP     edf_strict     : EDF bipartite + cheapest-insert  (default)\nH_STAB     commit_once    : hard sticky, no reassign\nH_RECOV    orphan_first   : orphan rescue pass, then bipartite",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "originalText": "Paradigm library   (5 hormones -> 5 allocators; ONE selected)\n\nH_SPATIAL  spatial_greedy : nearest-feasible + reject\nH_CRIT     priority_first : priority-tiered LSA\nH_TEMP     edf_strict     : EDF bipartite + cheapest-insert  (default)\nH_STAB     commit_once    : hard sticky, no reassign\nH_RECOV    orphan_first   : orphan rescue pass, then bipartite",
      "lineHeight": 1.3,
      "baseline": 15
    },
    {
