      "version": 1,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782051500909,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Cost matrix  C^(p)   +   LSA assignment\n\nC[r,t] = w_d.T + w_u.u^-1 + w_pi.pi^-1 + w_e.e + w_rho.rho\nfeasibility mask (arrival > deadline => inf);  queue cap  sum x <= Q\nx* = argmin_x  sum C^(p)[r,t] . x[r,t]      (Hungarian, O(N^3))",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "originalText": "Cost matrix  C^(p)   +   LSA assignment\n\nC[r,t] = w_d.T + w_u.u^-1 + w_pi.pi^-1 + w_e.e + w_rho.rho\nfeasibility mask (arrival > deadline => inf);  queue cap  sum x <= Q\nx* = argmin_x  sum C^(p)[r,t] . x[r,t]      (Hungarian, O(N^3))",
      "lineHeight": 1.3,
      "baseline": 15
    },
