      "text": "State Prototypes  V_i\n\n            td   ra   dp   fr\nSPATIAL    0.7  0.7  0.1  0.1\nCRIT       0.3  0.5  0.8  0.2\nTEMP       0.5  0.5  0.9  0.1\nSTAB       0.3  0.3  0.3  0.8\nRECOV      0.3  0.2  0.2  0.9",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "originalText": "State Prototypes  V_i\n\n            td   ra   dp   fr\nSPATIAL    0.7  0.7  0.1  0.1\nCRIT       0.3  0.5  0.8  0.2\nTEMP       0.5  0.5  0.9  0.1\nSTAB       0.3  0.3  0.3  0.8\nRECOV      0.3  0.2  0.2  0.9",
